## ğŸ“Š Project Overview

- **Dataset**: [Marketing Campaign Data (Kaggle)](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/imakash3011/customer-personality-analysis)
- **Tools Used**: Python (Pandas, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib), Tableau Public
- **Techniques**:
  - Data cleaning & preprocessing
  - Feature scaling with `StandardScaler`
  - Dimensionality reduction with `PCA`
  - Clustering with `KMeans` (Elbow method used to determine optimal `k`)
  - Cluster interpretation and labeling

